00:00:43.040 --> 00:00:47.820
SURE, RATS AND CATS ARE VERY DIFFERENT SPECIES,
HOWEVER, THIS STUDY LEADS RESEARCHERS TO BELIEVE

00:00:47.820 --> 00:00:49.030
